{"route":{"route":"/posts/931c13a4/","outputPath":"posts/931c13a4/index.html","kind":"post","title":"GeoIP mmdb format","language":"en","params":{"abbrlink":"931c13a4"}},"description":"complete document MaxMind DB File Format SpecificationDescription here is only how convert trie tree to array trie array left is 0, right is 1 value is index of","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/GeoIP-mmdb-format.md","route":"/posts/931c13a4/","abbrlink":"931c13a4","title":"GeoIP mmdb format","date":"2020-07-27 22:15:17","updated":"2020-07-27 22:15:17","tags":["Network"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"en","htmlLang":"en","locale":"en_US","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"en-US","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>complete document <a href=\"https://maxmind.github.io/MaxMind-DB/\">MaxMind DB File Format SpecificationDescription</a></p>\n<p>here is only how convert trie tree to array</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">0100, 1011 -&gt; trie</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">              root</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">               |</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">         +-----+------+</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        /              \\</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">       0                1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">     /   \\             /  \\</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">   null   1           0   null</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">         / \\        /   \\</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        0 null     null   1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">       / \\               / \\</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">       0 null         null  1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"></span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>trie -&gt; array<br>\nleft is 0, right is 1<br>\nvalue is index of array</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> left | right  byte/index</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">2     |   4    0-1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">null  |   6    2-3</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">8     |  null  4-5</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">10    |  null  6-7</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">null  |  12    8-9</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">14    |  null  10-11</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">null  |  16    11-12</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">end   |  null  12-13</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">null  |  end   13-14</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">array: [2,4,null,6,8,null,10,null,null,12,14,null,null,16,end,null,null,end]</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>for example:</p>\n<p>index 1:<br>\nnext left index 2 is null, so 00* is not exist<br>\nnext right index 2+1 = 3 is not null, continue search until end or null</p>\n<p>this is one byte as one child, but one byte max is 255, if node more than 255, we can use multiple byte as one child</p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"931c13a4","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}